{"questionId":"3588200","questionHtml":"<p>Given that she will still make pendulums for a total of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>15</mn></math> days, calculate the minimum integer value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> required for her to reach her target.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>attempt to use either arithmetic series formula equated to <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1000</mn></math>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <em><strong>(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>15</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>+</mo><mo>(</mo><mn>15</mn><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>)</mo><mo>×</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1000</mn></math>&nbsp; <strong>OR&nbsp;</strong> <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mn>15</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>(</mo><mn>10</mn><mo>+</mo><msub><mi>u</mi><mn>15</mn></msub><mo>)</mo><mo>=</mo><mn>1000</mn></math></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>09523</mn><mo>…</mo></math> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong> (A1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>9</mn></math> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong> A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> Follow through within question part for final <em><strong>A1</strong></em> for candidates correctly rounding their value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi></math> up to the nearest integer. Award <em><strong>(M0)(A0)A0</strong></em> for a response of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn></math> with no working shown.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>[3 marks]</strong></em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"3588200","referenceCode":"23M.2.SL.TZ2.2c","subjectId":"51-dp-mathematics-applications-and-interpretation","title":"Given that she will still make pendulums for a total of 15 days, calculate the minimum integer value of x required for her to reach her target.","paper":"2","level":"SL","questionNumber":"c","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 3]","breadcrumbLabels":["Topic 1—Number and algebra","Topic 1—Number and algebra","SL 1.2—Arithmetic sequences and series"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}